PropertyDbl _propKNP [protected]

Normal stiffness constant.

This constant is not to be confused with the instantaneous stiffness.

PropertyDbl _propKNV [protected]

Normal viscosity constant.

This constant is not to be confused with the instantaneous viscosity.

PropertyDbl _propPowerNP [protected]

Stiffness power- power to which normal spring displacement is raised.

The power is 1.0 by default.

PropertyDbl _propPowerNV [protected]

Viscosity power- power to which normal spring velocity is raised.

The power is 1.0 by default.
